WEBVTT

25:15.990 --> 25:17.480 line:80%
that the Imperial Court forbids
paying respects to the Marquis of Wu'an?

25:17.480 --> 25:18.240 line:80%
Well...

25:20.300 --> 25:22.570 line:80%
My Lord, you are a top scholar.

25:22.590 --> 25:23.450 line:80%
